//darkenn.homestead.com/files/inny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd Happening in Hate Last Night</span><hr size=1> <br>Wow, that's pretty cool.  Can they make the rog epic any easier? :P<br><br>My guess is 1) its a bug or 2) a stealth change with the last patch.  I doubt this was intended tho.  *shrugs* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uturlo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Turlo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 6:53:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13770.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd Happening in Hate Last Night</span><hr size=1> Possibly the first book was up long enough it double-popped?  This seems most likely, imo.  I saw a vender in Shadowhaven that had a similiar problem...you walk near the south part of zone and you start lagging bad.  I fought my way through it and saw dozens of the same vender stacked on each other.  And that's only what I could figure out.  Was fixed a few patches later. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uandrewbb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AndrewBB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 12:32:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13770.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.mindspring.com/~dnorris/impman.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd Happening in Hate Last Night</span><hr size=1> Typically the book gets picked up by a wandering mob before it repops, or at least it _can_. My guess is that the building was kept clear long enough that it had a chance to pop twice.<br><br>I doubt they added code to make this 'ground spawn' depop on its own when a wanderer would typically pick it up at some point. <br><br>Other possibility is of course that they broke something, and the wanderer no longer picks it up. But I doubt it. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81313">Andrewe</a> -Lvl 56 Enchanter, Bristlebane [Cry of War]</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unosrednassor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nosredna Ssor</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 12:35:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13770.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd Happening in Hate Last Night</span><hr size=1> The time between my looting of the book and my friend looting the book was under 5 seconds.  I looted mine and another was immidiately sitting on the table.  I pointed this out to my friend who was standing beside me and she then looted it.<br><br>Cheers,<br><br>Nos <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upatofnaud.showPublicProfile?language=EN>patofnaud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 2:42:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13770.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd Happening in Hate Last Night</span><hr size=1> &quot;Typically the book gets picked up by a wandering mob before it repops, or at least it _can_. &quot;<br><br>Nope, not for almost a year. That was a verifiable bug that Kendrick fixed.<br><br>My guess is you were the beneficiary of a spawn glitch. Rejoice but don't expect to see it again anytime soon.<br><br>Kinda like finding that 2nd $20 stuck to the one you got from the ATM machine.<br><br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><body lang=EN-US style='tab-interval:.5in'><div class=Section1><font face="Verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2"><P><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=22671">Patofnaud</a><br>55th Season Redeemed Epic Shadow Dweller<br> <span style='color:black'>Warden of something or other.<br><I>(We work in shadows, we dress in black.)</I><br></span><P>Patofwaan Griffonbate<br>44th Season Friend Of Wolves <br>Guild Leader of Karma<br><P>Patofwarr Barbarian Warrior<br>21st Season Soldier of Rallos Zek<br><p><span style='color:lime'>All proud members of <a href="http://www.geocities.com/karmaofmorellthule">Karma</a> Guild, In the Land of Morell-Thule<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulillianasweetleaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lilliana Sweetleaf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 4:47:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13770.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </